## User / Author / Post is verified condition

**User is verified** condition checks if the current user has a verified profile, **Author is verified** checks if the post author has a verified profile. **Post is verified** checks if the current post is verified

Profiles can be verified in **WP-admin > Users > Profiles (Voxel) > Edit Profile > Verification status** metabox

## Example

Author is verified condition can be used to put a verified checkmark next to the username, on the user profile.
